{"tid":384890,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚從事醫療業既巴絲同讀醫科即既巴絲入黎，有問題請教下","createTime":"2017-09-02T16:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T18:13:18.000Z","uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f9c62a8b5fa2f459e35c7d5c2c23c1e167422e9","tid":384890,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"如果覺得右下腹痛楚出現左，通常係咩原因引致右下腹痛楚加劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望你地個答案值得參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個問題係認真問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2462ec3eaf16b788b1621a16372fdcdeb5dd9a34","tid":384890,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"盲腸炎 腸炎 腸塞 便秘痛"},{"pid":"ac303dd54191dab4f22716f341da557c6dbf2b1a","tid":384890,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:56:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盲腸炎 腸炎 腸塞 便秘痛</blockquote><br />\n明白，想問多個<br />\n如果係右上腹痛呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4f4fdb71377a4c4cb1a74a98079dc5deb733fc","tid":384890,"uid":85504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>盲腸炎 腸炎 腸塞 便秘痛</blockquote><br />\n明白，想問多個<br />\n如果係右上腹痛呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肝"},{"pid":"d6a433f964e597cb178fdfec4fd278b225b1d0a8","tid":384890,"uid":39565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>盲腸炎 腸炎 腸塞 便秘痛</blockquote><br />\n明白，想問多個<br />\n如果係右上腹痛呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肝炎 (甲乙丙）<br />\n膽管炎 膽囊炎"},{"pid":"e5a57c981997100710a87fdf7840ff530e4ec086","tid":384890,"uid":39565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果覺得右下腹痛楚出現左，通常係咩原因引致右下腹痛楚加劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望你地個答案值得參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個問題係認真問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbtw 肚痛+ 陰道出血 (女仔）<br />\n會諗埋 宮外孕"},{"pid":"e6003f9202581232758ef06772382f2cdb1ce165","tid":384890,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>盲腸炎 腸炎 腸塞 便秘痛</blockquote><br />\n明白，想問多個<br />\n如果係右上腹痛呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肝炎 (甲乙丙）<br />\n膽管炎 膽囊炎</blockquote><br />\n甲乙丙都有分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e21c58ae78888ac68a7617413ffd0010e0a61d","tid":384890,"uid":68753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:21:09.000Z","msg":"右下腹痛係症狀<br />\n背後應該有原因 e.g. 盲腸炎, 便秘, 婦科病<br />\n唔同既病會係唔同既情況下加劇腹痛<br />\n所以應該係掉返轉, 病人講返自己咩情況下會痛多痛少左, 作為搵diagnosis既線索<br />\n之後臨床檢查再驗證"},{"pid":"d37cb96f1fb4a424cc9a599e3ff6cb936623a1c1","tid":384890,"uid":39565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:24:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>盲腸炎 腸炎 腸塞 便秘痛</blockquote><br />\n明白，想問多個<br />\n如果係右上腹痛呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肝炎 (甲乙丙）<br />\n膽管炎 膽囊炎</blockquote><br />\n甲乙丙都有分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n急性 會痛<br />\n好似急性甲肝咁<br />\n而乙肝，或者丙肝，一般係慢性（冇乜病徵，主要可能係好攰，冇乜胃口，作嘔作悶咁）<br />\n但乙/丙肝可以急性發作"},{"pid":"36c1f74417311af198b343807f44e4faf164947f","tid":384890,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>盲腸炎 腸炎 腸塞 便秘痛</blockquote><br />\n明白，想問多個<br />\n如果係右上腹痛呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肝炎 (甲乙丙）<br />\n膽管炎 膽囊炎</blockquote><br />\n甲乙丙都有分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n急性 會痛<br />\n好似急性甲肝咁<br />\n而乙肝，或者丙肝，一般係慢性（冇乜病徵，主要可能係好攰，冇乜胃口，作嘔作悶咁）<br />\n但乙/丙肝可以急性發作</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個痛會唔會隔一段時間再痛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57824f8f4ea0dcc9bd04d41258b268b426bf5deb","tid":384890,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>盲腸炎 腸炎 腸塞 便秘痛</blockquote><br />\n明白，想問多個<br />\n如果係右上腹痛呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肝炎 (甲乙丙）<br />\n膽管炎 膽囊炎</blockquote><br />\n胃炎 胃潰瘍 十二指腸炎"},{"pid":"559919e8da089a2e0843c9324ba08f3f64dd6428","tid":384890,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:13:18.000Z","msg":"講咁多都無謂，可能性太多，唔舒服快啲去睇醫生做檢查，起碼照個超聲波"}]}